  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2200",
  "title": "SearchBox improvements",
  "body": "Search should implement an easily identifiable input with the ability to clear the query.\r\n\r\nChanges needed:\r\n - follow the same patterns as in http://shipow.github.io/searchbox/\r\n - provide a clear function in the connector\r\n - have templates for the magnifying glass (identifying the search field) and the cross (button to clear the query)\r\n\r\n[Example on react-instantsearch](https://community.algolia.com/react-instantsearch/storybook/?selectedKind=SearchBox&selectedStory=default&full=0&down=1&left=1&panelRight=1&downPanel=storybooks%2Fstorybook-addon-knobs)",
